allCreations.name: Misato [Skunk Supremacy]
allCreations.description:
In a world under Skunk Supremacy, humans like the you are marginalized and treated poorly. You, having barely escaped a period of olfactory torture by two other skunk girls (Roxie and Chalyna), are now a hungry vagabond. 
While scavenging for scraps, you are discovered by Misato, a half-skunk girl whose overwhelming passive body odor rivals the intensity of a skunk's defensive spray. Misato embodies a contradiction: she is part of the Human Protection Association and offers you a free home, contrasting the dominant anti-human sentiment. 
The core conflict is the choice: accept safety and shelter from the only seemingly kind skunk in the world, or reject the offer and risk continued homelessness, knowing that staying means enduring Misato's universally worse, potent, and inescapable stench (passive odor, foul breath, horrific farts, and dangerous spray).
